create table admin_audit_logs (admin_user_id bigint not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, target_user_id bigint, timestamp datetime(6) not null, action varchar(50) not null, details TEXT, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB
create table brkodu (BRKODU varchar(20) not null, BRKDAC varchar(255), primary key (BRKODU)) engine=InnoDB

create table entry_exit_records (latitude float(53), longitude float(53), created_at datetime(6) not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, timestamp datetime(6) not null, user_id bigint not null, ip_address varchar(45), qr_code_value varchar(255) not null, type enum ('ENTRY','EXIT') not null, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB

create table excuses (excuse_date date not null, excuse_type_id bigint not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, reviewed_at datetime(6), reviewed_by bigint, submitted_at datetime(6) not null, user_id bigint not null, excuse_type_name varchar(100) not null, description TEXT, admin_notes TEXT, attachments TEXT, status enum ('APPROVED','PENDING','REJECTED') not null, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB

create table ip_address_logs (admin_user_id bigint, created_at datetime(6) not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, timestamp datetime(6) not null, user_id bigint not null, ip_address varchar(45), details JSON, action enum ('ACCESS','ASSIGN','MISMATCH','REMOVE','VIEW') not null, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB

create table otp_verifications (verified bit not null, otp_code varchar(6) not null, created_at datetime(6) not null, expires_at datetime(6) not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, tc_no varchar(11) not null, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB

create table person (esicno bigint not null, tckiml varchar(11) not null, brkodu varchar(20), unvkod varchar(20), peradi varchar(100) not null, soyadi varchar(100) not null, primary key (esicno)) engine=InnoDB

create table qr_codes (usage_count integer not null, valid_date date not null, created_at datetime(6) not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, user_id bigint not null, version bigint, qr_code_value varchar(255) not null, primary key (id), check ((usage_count>=0) and (usage_count<=2))) engine=InnoDB
create table telefo (esicno bigint, id bigint not null auto_increment, telefo varchar(15), primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB
create table unvkod (unvkod varchar(20) not null, unvack varchar(255), primary key (unvkod)) engine=InnoDB

create table users (created_at datetime(6) not null, id bigint not null auto_increment, last_login_at datetime(6), updated_at datetime(6) not null, department_code varchar(10), title_code varchar(10), tc_no varchar(11) not null, mobile_phone varchar(15) not null, personnel_no varchar(20) not null, first_name varchar(100) not null, last_name varchar(100) not null, department_name varchar(200), assigned_ip_addresses TEXT, password_hash varchar(255) not null, role enum ('ADMIN','NORMAL_USER','SUPER_ADMIN') not null, primary key (id)) engine=InnoDB
